                    <div className="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 p-5 rounded-xl mb-6 flex flex-col space-y-3">
                        <div className="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <Info className="text-red-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" size={16} />
                            <div className="text-[11px] text-red-200/90 leading-relaxed">
                                <p className="font-bold mb-2 text-sm text-red-400">🚨 彻底解决 404/Localhost 错误：</p>
                                <p className="mb-2">您的项目 Site URL 仍指向本地。请前往 Supabase 后台修改：</p>
                                <ol className="list-decimal list-inside space-y-1 ml-1">
                                    <li>登录 Supabase &rarr; Authentication</li>
                                    <li>URL Configuration &rarr; <strong>Site URL</strong></li>
                                    <li>修改为: <code className="bg-black/40 px-1 rounded">https://yuzhibi-ai-writin.pages.dev</code></li>
